Package: gfaR
Type: Package
Title: Genomic Feature Analyzer for Non-B DNA Motifs
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jason Ciemielewski
Maintainer: Jason Ciemielewski <jason@example.com>
Description: Refactored R package version of the Genomic Feature Analyzer (GFA) 
    C-program for finding non-B DNA motifs in nucleic acid sequences. The 
    original GFA citation is Regina Z. Cer, Duncan E. Donohue, Uma S. Mudunuri, 
    Nuri A. Temiz, Michael A. Loss, Nathan J. Starner, Goran N. Halusa, Natalia 
    Volfovsky, Ming Yi, Brian T. Luke, Albino Bacolla, Jack R. Collins and 
    Robert M. Stephens. Nucl. Acids Res. (2013) 41 (D1): D94-D100. 
    doi: 10.1093/nar/gks955.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: Rcpp
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
